  "rule_text": "The button is centered in the lower-middle below the headline. Fill Deep Blue #003D74, white label (Nunito Sans 800, 18px), with a Gold #FFC20E arrow `\u203a` (24px) after two non-breaking spaces. Size 248 \u00d7 64px.",
